content:
This is the Digital Insurance Platform Consultant Learning Journey:

Get Started with the Digital Insurance Platform
Learn OmniStudio
Go Deeper into Digital Insurance Platform Components
Keep Learning!

Step 1: Get Started with the Digital Insurance Platform

* Earn Salesforce Sales Cloud and Service Cloud Consultant Credentials
* Digital Insurance Platform Foundations
* Digital Insurance Platform Demo
* Claims Management Demo
* Learn Insurance Foundations:
	+ The Insurance Industry
	+ Insurance Quoting Foundations
	+ Individual Insurance Policy Administration Foundations
	+ Group Insurance Contracts and Enrollments Foundations
	+ Insurance Claims Foundations
	+ Insurance Data Model

Step 2: Learn OmniStudio

* Get Trained with OmniOut or Design and Administer an OmniStudio Solution
* Study and Prepare:
	+ OmniStudio Consultant Exam Guide
	+ OmniStudio Consultant Trailmix
* Get Certified! Schedule Your OmniStudio Consultant Exam

Step 3: Go Deeper into Digital Insurance Platform Components

* Explore Insurance Quoting:
	+ Get to Know Insurance Quoting
	+ Insurance Quoting Documentation
* Learn Product Modeling:
	+ Insurance Product Modeling
	+ Design Product Models for Insurance Applications
* Learn about the Digital Insurance Application Suites:
	+ Insurance Property & Casualty Application Documentation
	+ Group Voluntary Benefits Application Documentation

Step 4: Keep Learning!

* Learn About Contracts and Document Generation:
	+ Get to Know Industries Contract Lifecycle Management
	+ Contract Lifecycle Management Documentation
* Learn about Business Rules Engine:
	+ Business Rules Engine
	+ Business Rules Engine Documentation
title: Salesforce Insurance Platform Training
